Pritesh and Mansi Gandhi started trying for a baby ten years ago but repeatedly lost the babies . 
  Pritesh's sister Hiral Shah offered to carry the couple's baby after IVF treatment . 
  Mansi became pregnant in 2007 but the boy was so premature he died after a six-month fight for life . 
  The couple suffered five miscarriages and lost six babies in total . 
  Hiral gave birth to baby Krish three weeks ago after a 20-minute labour . 
 